        <h1>Flu Symptoms</h1>
    </div>
    <p>
        Flu symptoms often come on suddenly. People who have the flu often feel some or all of these symptoms:
    </p>
    <ul class="symptom-list">
        <li>Fever or feeling feverish/chills</li>
        <li>Cough</li>
        <li>Sore throat</li>
        <li>Runny or stuffy nose</li>
        <li>Muscle or body aches</li>
        <li>Headaches</li>
        <li>Fatigue (tiredness)</li>
        <li>Some people may have vomiting and diarrhea, though this is more common in children than adults.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

